About Event

​Join bio founders, investors, operators, scientists, researchers, and enthusiasts for a quick “sweatworking” session. Come get a workout in before the JPM Healthcare Conference week kicks off and meet new people in the healthcare industry. Feel free to jog and/or walk at your own conversational pace. Dogs are welcome! All fitness levels are welcome too!
